Package: VisCello
Type: Package
Title: A visualization tool for single cell data of C.elegans embrogenesis
Version: 0.9.0
Author: Qin Zhu, Jonathan Packer, Junyhong Kim, John Murray, Bob Waterston
Maintainer: Qin Zhu <zhuqin@pennmedicine.upenn.edu>
Description: A visualization tool for C.elegans scRNA-Seq data. Also applicable to other scRNA-Seq/scATAC-Seq data as a hosting, exploration and analysis platfrom (see VisCello.base). 
